<div class= "wrapper"><div class= "box signin-box centered">

  <div class="row">
    <div class="active">
      <h2 class= "no-margin centered darkblue"><a  id="login-form-link">Starting the Process</a></h2>
      <hr>
      <br>
      <div class='liquidate-info'>
        Please fill in the form to send your request to a DreamFunded team member. All information will be kept confidential. <br><br> Questions? Go to our education center <a href= "/education"><u>here</u></a>.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class= "login-container">
    <%= form_tag('liquidate_form', :method => :post, :id => "liquidate_form") do %>
      <%= text_field_tag(:first_name, nil, :class =>"userbox half", :placeholder => "First name", :required => true) %>
      <%= text_field_tag(:last_name, nil, :class =>"userbox half scoot-left", :placeholder => "Last name", :required => true) %>
      <%= text_field_tag(:email, nil, :class =>"userbox half", :placeholder => "Email", :required => true) %>
      <%= text_field_tag(:phone, nil, :class =>"userbox half scoot-left", :placeholder => "Phone") %>
      <%= text_field_tag(:company, nil, :class =>"userbox", :placeholder => "Company", :required => true) %>
      <%= number_field_tag(:number_shares, nil, :class =>"userbox", :placeholder => "Quantity of shares") %>
<!--       <div class="input-symbol">
        <span>
          &#36;
        </span> -->
        <%= number_field_tag(:shares_price, nil, :class =>"userbox", :placeholder => "Desired share price", :required => true) %>
<!--       </div>
 -->
      <%= select_tag(:timeframe, options_for_select([ "< 1 Week", "< 1 Month", "1 Month or More" ]), prompt: "Timeframe") %>
      <br>
      <br>
      <%= check_box_tag(:rofr_restrictions, nil, false) %>
      My company has ROFR restrictions (right of first refusal).
      <!-- <a class="tooltip" href="/education/basics">ROFR<span class="warning">Dreamfunded can help you sell your shares immediately -- and avoid your company's restrictions!</span></a>
      restrictions (right of first refusal). -->
      <br>
      <br>
      <%= check_box_tag(:financial_assistance, nil, false) %>
      I may need financial help to exercise (purchase) shares from my employer (company).
      <!-- <a class="tooltip" href="/education/basics">purchase<span class="help">We offer financial assistance in order to allow you to exercise your shares!</span></a>
      shares from my company. -->

      <%= text_area(:message, nil, rows: 5, :class =>"userbox", :placeholder => "Comments") %>
      <br>
        <div class = "notice centered">
          <h2 class='darkblue' ><%= flash[:notice] if flash[:notice] %></h2>
        </div>
      <div class= "centered">
        <%= submit_tag("Submit", :class => "login-button") %>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>

</div>
